    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Prayer of Healing</strong> (Level 2 Evocation)</p><p>Up to six creatures of your choice that you can see within range each regain hit points equal to 2d8 + your spellcasting ability modifier. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the healing increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 10 minutes | <strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric</em></p>",
